Package eu.profinit.manta.connector.erstudio.model

Interface ErStudioSolution

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ErStudioSolutionImpl
    public interface ErStudioSolution
    An ErStudioSolution interface provides an access to a Logical and set of Physical models and their underlying DataObjects. The interface's realization may be an internal Data Model that is loaded directly from a ErStudioFile, or may be an external one whose origin is in a different .DM1 file and is only some of its objects are referenced from the ErStudioFile was loaded from. Every DataModel in ErStudioSolution must have a unique name. For Entities and Tables of type CompositeDataObject belonging to some model, pair Owner & the object's name must be unique. For Attributes and Columns of type SimpleDataObject must have unique name across their parents of type CompositeDataObject
